召開內部會議，副總裁鄭麗矜喺會上提到，之後嘅日子會艱難，要見步行步，又叫同事諗定自己條底線，如果接受唔到「就要諗吓」，仲話如果同事有好路數走，佢唔會阻攔。有同事亦關心鄭麗矜嘅去向，鄭強調自己身體健康、家庭幸福，一定唔會辭職，如果有日離開Now新聞台，大家可以問點解。</strong>"},{"pid":"dbe9d50306888fa385565bb63f942474d6c5ede1","tid":2071597,"uid":20170,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-20T03:21:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"32b6acb9fae23b27842affd621611e2dcc004b74","tid":2071597,"uid":273703,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-20T03:21:31.000Z","msg":"理大圍城果陣中左火魔果位CCTVB 同事近況點？"},{"pid":"22cff0e0ae022f607450e63b1670b708f99bc0f4","tid":2071597,"uid":288312,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-20T03:39:08.000Z","msg":"[法律戰線救手足] 打甩暴動罪!<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/fBrPHS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/fBrPHS</a>"},{"pid":"6257576fde342520e109e10fb421c0db9896dd1a","tid":2071597,"uid":2267,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-20T03:42:30.000Z","msg":"屌，啱先續兩年約<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4cb470a4b6b0276de2a976134a55d74a17d6e91e","tid":2071597,"uid":20867,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-20T03:44:41.000Z","msg":"「當他們侵蝕ATV的時候，我沒有發聲。」"},{"pid":"bff9cc882980076101bcc1aa72df772d3edd10f4","tid":2071597,"uid":18477,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-20T03:44:44.000Z","msg":"傻㗎咩<br />\n仲乜可以咁撚樣話空降就空降<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"726625513289fe29242841a577628ca19cd940ee","tid":2071597,"uid":55089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-20T03:45:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.